SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_GLUTTONY_FOOD_000_CUT_.text:
Well, yee-haw! Now let's make ourselves scarce;
if I gotta smell those stinking hogs for one more
second, I won't be able to keep my lunch down.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_SLOTH_HELP_000_CUT_010.text:
Er, I meeean...he hates noise! I don't know
if you could call it a weakness, exactly,
but loud noises send him right to sleep.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_ALL_SLOTH_NOTHING_000_.text:
Blast! The key's right next to his pillow;
I don't think we can grab it without
waking him in the process.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_BABY_RUIN_000_CUT_000_.text:
I am the Dismal King;
naught transpires in Yomi
that I do not know of.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_BABY_FLY_000_CUT_000_1.text:
We only came here to find a triangle;
we don't gotta stick our necks out
for anything beyond that.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_BABY_SLOTH_100_CUT_000.text:
My thralls have cleared the way;
we need not go to the trouble of
meeting the Warden of Sloth.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_BABY_LUST_100_CUT_000_.text:
My thralls have cleared the way;
we need not go to the trouble of
meeting the Warden of Lust.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_BABY_GLUTTONY_100_CUT_.text:
My thralls have cleared the way;
we need not go to the trouble of
meeting the Warden of Gluttony.

SUB_W03_EVAR_BOFO_BABY_LUST_000_CUT_000_.text:
A king is a supreme being;
one not bound by concepts like
responsibility or freedom.
